Phase 3 - Development and Implementation
----------------------------------------

Security Activities
• Secure coding practices
• Static code analysis
• Dependency scanning
• Secret management
• Code review with security focus

Tools & Technologies
• SAST: SonarQube, Checkmarx, Veracode, Fortify
• SCA: Snyk, WhiteSource, Black Duck
• Secret scanning: GitGuardian, TruffleHog
• IDE plugins: SonarLint, Snyk plugin
• Git hooks for pre-commit checks

Methodologies & Standards
• OWASP Secure Coding Practices
• Peer code review with security checklist
• Shift-left security
• DevSecOps practices
• Secure SDLC training

Key Deliverables
• Clean SAST scan results
• Dependency vulnerability report
• Code review sign-offs
• Security unit tests
